snippet.title: Ricochet Kills: Noir - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Ricochet Kills: Noir on: http://store.steampowered.com/app/596630/

Ricochet Kills: Noir. It is a puzzle-shooter game in original minimalistic noir style. Use bullets ricochets to kill your enemies and keep in mind that your ammo is limited. Try your skills on 100 different levels.

Games reviews and download: http://download.online-games.co/
